    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AuthController
    Interface for authentication control across all user types.
    CareerCenterStaff
    Represents a career center staff member who extends the base `User`.
    CareerCenterStaffController
    Controller used by career center staff to perform administrative actions.
    CareerCenterStaffView
    View layer for Career Center Staff user interface.
    CompanyApprovalStatus
    Enumeration representing the approval status of a company representative.
    CompanyRepresentative
    Represents a company representative user who can post and manage internships.
    CompanyRepresentativeController
    Controller used by company representatives to manage internships and applications.
    CompanyRepresentativeView
    View layer for Company Representative user interface.
    DataStore
    Singleton in-memory repository for application data.
    Internship
     
    InternshipApplication
     
    InternshipLevel
    Enumeration representing the difficulty or experience level of an internship.
    InternshipStatus
    Enumeration representing the status of an internship or internship application.
    InternshipWithdrawalStatus
    Enumeration representing the status of an internship withdrawal request.
    IReportGenerator
    Interface for generating internship reports based on specified criteria.
    LoginResult
    Enumeration representing the result of a login attempt.
    ProjectApp
    Entry point for the internship-management project CLI.
    ReportCriteria
    Encapsulates criteria for filtering and sorting internship reports.
    ReportGenerator
    Generates internship reports by filtering and sorting based on specified criteria.
    ReportSortType
    Enumeration representing sorting options for internship reports.
    Student
    Represents a student user in the system.
    StudentController
    Controller used by students to search internships, manage applications, and accept/withdraw from offers.
    StudentView
    View layer for Student user interface.
    User
    Abstract base class representing a user in the system.
    UserView
    Abstract base view class for all user types.
    viewApplication
    Interface for viewing internship application information.
    viewInternship
    Interface for viewing internship information.
